{"tid":971921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"世上令人最痛的十大昆虫","createTime":"2019-01-07T04:25:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T15:46:05.000Z","uid":25345,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"180037c4690fb548ec25502370abab5fc145813f","tid":971921,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:25:40.000Z","msg":"大部分的人都會覺得被蜂蜇到很痛，幸運的是，被食蛛鷹蜂或火蟻咬到的那種超可怖的痛，我們大多數人可以避免；不過，美國昆蟲學家賈斯汀施密特(Justin Schmidt)非常投入研究昆蟲，還親身體驗各種被咬的痛，指出其中有3種痛感，和147種灼熱感。 <br />\n<br />\n施密特是亞利桑納州大學(University of Arizona)的昆蟲學家，他實地考察、挖掘昆蟲的居住地，而讓這些蟲子很不爽，便把毒牙、刺或螯狠狠地刺向他。 <br />\n<br />\n儘管如此，「no pain, no gain」(沒有痛苦，哪來收獲)這句話用在這裡，再適合不過了，施密特把他的痛苦指數(Schmidt Sting Pain Index)變成經驗談，將78種昆蟲納入排行榜，主觀認定有多痛。 <br />\n<br />\n十大最痛咬傷如下： <br />\n<br />\n第十名：汗蜂(Sweat Bee)，等級：1.0，疼痛很輕微、短暫，感覺像小火花把手臂的一根汗毛燒掉。 <br />\n<br />\n第九名：火蟻(Fire Ant)，等級：1.2，很強烈、有點驚人。 <br />\n<br />\n第八名：牛角相思樹蟻(Bullhorn Acacia Ant)，等級：1.8，罕見的刺痛，發麻的刺痛，像有人在你臉上訂了訂書針。 <br />\n<br />\n第七名：大黃蜂(Bald-Faced Hornet)，等級2.0，深層強烈的痛感，像手被轉動的門壓到。 <br />\n<br />\n▲十大最痛咬傷的第六名到第一名。(圖／取自英國《每日郵報》) <br />\n<br />\n第六名：小黃蜂(Yellow Jacket)，等級2.0，灼熱感，像有人把雪茄在你的舌頭上弄熄。 <br />\n<br />\n第五名：蜜蜂(Honey Bee)，等級2.0，像火柴摩擦你的皮膚而且燃燒。 <br />\n<br />\n第四名：紅收獲蟻(Red Harvester Ant)，等級：3.0，粗魯無情，像有人用鑽子挖進向內生長的腳指甲。 <br />\n<br />\n第三名：長腳蜂(Paper Wasp)，等級：3.0，像一大杯鹽酸灑在傷口。 <br />\n<br />\n第二名：食蛛鷹蜂，等級：4.0，讓人暈眩，像使用中的吹風機掉進你正在泡的浴缸。 <br />\n<br />\n第一名：子彈蟻(Bullet Ant)，等級：4+，像走過燒得火熱的木炭，同時有3吋生鏽的鐵釘刺進腳後跟。 <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/92/92572.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F92%2F92572.jpg&h=8f0627c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a540f3f289b06a11462bb29b21adb42556e4d56f","tid":971921,"uid":69083,"like":43,"dislike":2,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:37:04.000Z","msg":"邊撚柒到支那鄉下  唔撚識寫個「蟲」字?"},{"pid":"a98b07a7a56592cd37fdd56f7dbc6a3b03bd120f","tid":971921,"uid":182499,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:37:10.000Z","msg":"全部都係蜂同蟻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"250025793adeb7bbd39f72f53821ab706ace99f5","tid":971921,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:48:19.000Z","msg":"睇啲形容都覺得驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3835db229e5d4952819d4c6aee23baf493af62ad","tid":971921,"uid":52155,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:51:12.000Z","msg":"最痛<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">恨</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">蝗</span></span>蟲"},{"pid":"82d0601880b85c762ea992876dc08792ddcdcbe4","tid":971921,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:52:40.000Z","msg":"蜜蜂竟然排第五？"},{"pid":"399c068d5a717012dbcb252cdd3e75075a8665a5","tid":971921,"uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:53:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20120123/photo/0123-00174-001b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20120123%2Fphoto%2F0123-00174-001b2.jpg&h=f8221dc4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a39003a93b2760e8d20b043424c620d22e3fb0eb","tid":971921,"uid":40318,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:56:47.000Z","msg":"第一：蝗蟲(Chinese)，等級：40++，所過之處，寸草不生。"},{"pid":"307f18dbf25faea71248beed761c6e8472a675ac","tid":971921,"uid":158933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82d0601880b85c762ea992876dc08792ddcdcbe4","tid":971921,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:52:40.000Z","msg":"蜜蜂竟然排第五？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:58:38.000Z","msg":"原來已經好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"784b2f23568fab876262d05c5d0cd82e8209405f","tid":971921,"uid":33848,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T05:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src